experience: Some previous work-related skill, knowledge, or experience is usually needed. For example, a teller would benefit from experience working directly with the public.
education: These occupations usually require a high school diploma.
job_training: Employees in these occupations need anywhere from a few months to one year of working with experienced employees. A recognized apprenticeship program may be associated with these occupations.
example: These occupations often involve using your knowledge and skills to help others. Examples include orderlies, counter and rental clerks, customer service representatives, security guards, upholsterers, tellers, and dental laboratory technicians.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Examine blast areas to determine amounts and kinds of explosive charges needed and to ensure that safety laws are observed.
work_tasks.descr: Examine blast areas to determine amounts and kinds of explosive charges needed and to ensure that safety laws are observed.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Tie specified lengths of delaying fuses into patterns in order to time sequences of explosions.
work_tasks.descr: Tie specified lengths of delaying fuses into patterns in order to time sequences of explosions.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Place safety cones around blast areas to alert other workers of danger zones, and signal workers as necessary to ensure that they clear blast sites prior to explosions.
work_tasks.descr: Place safety cones around blast areas to alert other workers of danger zones, and signal workers as necessary to ensure that they clear blast sites prior to explosions.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Place explosive charges in holes or other spots; then detonate explosives to demolish structures or to loosen, remove, or displace earth, rock, or other materials.
work_tasks.descr: Place explosive charges in holes or other spots; then detonate explosives to demolish structures or to loosen, remove, or displace earth, rock, or other materials.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Insert, pack, and pour explosives, such as dynamite, ammonium nitrate, black powder, or slurries into blast holes; then shovel drill cuttings, admit water into boreholes, and tamp material to compact charges.
work_tasks.descr: Insert, pack, and pour explosives, such as dynamite, ammonium nitrate, black powder, or slurries into blast holes; then shovel drill cuttings, admit water into boreholes, and tamp material to compact charges.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Mark patterns, locations, and depths of charge holes for drilling, and issue drilling instructions.
work_tasks.descr: Mark patterns, locations, and depths of charge holes for drilling, and issue drilling instructions.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Compile and keep gun and explosives records in compliance with local and federal laws.
work_tasks.descr: Compile and keep gun and explosives records in compliance with local and federal laws.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Connect electrical wire to primers, and cover charges or fill blast holes with clay, drill chips, sand, or other material.
work_tasks.descr: Connect electrical wire to primers, and cover charges or fill blast holes with clay, drill chips, sand, or other material.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Measure depths of drilled blast holes, using weighted tape measures.
work_tasks.descr: Measure depths of drilled blast holes, using weighted tape measures.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Lay primacord between rows of charged blast holes, and tie cord into main lines to form blast patterns.
work_tasks.descr: Lay primacord between rows of charged blast holes, and tie cord into main lines to form blast patterns.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Assemble and position equipment, explosives, and blasting caps in holes at specified depths, or load perforating guns or torpedoes with explosives.
work_tasks.descr: Assemble and position equipment, explosives, and blasting caps in holes at specified depths, or load perforating guns or torpedoes with explosives.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Drive trucks to transport explosives and blasting equipment to blasting sites.
work_tasks.descr: Drive trucks to transport explosives and blasting equipment to blasting sites.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Cut specified lengths of primacord and attach primers to cord ends.
work_tasks.descr: Cut specified lengths of primacord and attach primers to cord ends.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Maintain inventory levels, ordering new supplies as necessary.
work_tasks.descr: Maintain inventory levels, ordering new supplies as necessary.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Clean, gauge, and lubricate gun ports.
work_tasks.descr: Clean, gauge, and lubricate gun ports.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Connect gun chambers to electric detonating devices, and operate controls at panelboards, in order to detonate charges in guns or to ignite chemical charges.
work_tasks.descr: Connect gun chambers to electric detonating devices, and operate controls at panelboards, in order to detonate charges in guns or to ignite chemical charges.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Verify detonation of charges by observing control panels, or by listening for the sounds of blasts.
work_tasks.descr: Verify detonation of charges by observing control panels, or by listening for the sounds of blasts.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Move and store inventories of explosives, loaded perforating guns, and other materials, according to established safety procedures.
work_tasks.descr: Move and store inventories of explosives, loaded perforating guns, and other materials, according to established safety procedures.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Light fuses, drop detonating devices into wells or boreholes, or activate firing devices with plungers, dials, or buttons, in order to set off single or multiple blasts.
work_tasks.descr: Light fuses, drop detonating devices into wells or boreholes, or activate firing devices with plungers, dials, or buttons, in order to set off single or multiple blasts.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Repair and service blasting, shooting, and automotive equipment, and electrical wiring and instruments, using hand tools.
work_tasks.descr: Repair and service blasting, shooting, and automotive equipment, and electrical wiring and instruments, using hand tools.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Set up and operate short-wave radio or field telephone equipment to transmit and receive blast information.
work_tasks.descr: Set up and operate short-wave radio or field telephone equipment to transmit and receive blast information.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Insert waterproof sealers, bullets, and/or powder charges into guns, and screw gun ports back into place.
work_tasks.descr: Insert waterproof sealers, bullets, and/or powder charges into guns, and screw gun ports back into place.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Insert powder charges into chambers of sidewall sample-taking cylinders, and assemble cylinders, using special wrenches.
work_tasks.descr: Insert powder charges into chambers of sidewall sample-taking cylinders, and assemble cylinders, using special wrenches.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Lower perforating guns into wells, using hoists; then use measuring devices and instrument panels to position guns in correct positions for taking samples.
work_tasks.descr: Lower perforating guns into wells, using hoists; then use measuring devices and instrument panels to position guns in correct positions for taking samples.

work_tasks.title: Explosives Workers, Ordnance Handling Experts, and Blasters
work_tasks.task: Obtain samples of earth from sidewalls of well boreholes, using electrically exploding devices.
work_tasks.descr: Obtain samples of earth from sidewalls of well boreholes, using electrically exploding devices.
